data.description: **NEW PRICE!!! NOW: $375K** LAKEFRONT!! Rare find on private Shadowood Lake, boasting approx. 200ft of water frontage & 3.737 acres! Surrounded by nature, beautiful wildlife & easy access to the city! No restrictions here so bring your livestock, ATV's, & enjoy bonfires! Overlooking the water, this 2015 modular home hardie plank siding has 2200+ square feet, 9ft high ceilings, 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths! Cozy open floor plan of main living room with a stacked stone fireplace, & dining area! Kitchen has bar top seating, stainless appliances including the fridge, & walk-in pantry! Throughout the common areas are 3/4' solid oak wood flooring! There's even an additional bonus room that includes a king size murphy bed, that can be used as a second family room or a game room! You'll love the split master bedroom! Wake up to window overviews of the glistening water! Step inside your master bath to find a large tiled walk-in shower offering 2 shower heads & natural light from the transom window above! You also have a walk-in closet, separate potty room, double sinks & plenty of storage! Nestled by the master is a spare room, ideal for an office space! On the opposite end of the home is the second family room/bonus room, 2 perfectly sized bedrooms, 2 full baths & laundry area! This is on Shadowood Lake, no HOA requirements with this gem! You're allowed all the fun water privileges of fishing/wake & knee boarding/skiing & tubing! Cast your line off your own personal dock, & see if you can catch the popular fish found here of, largemouth bass! Located just northeast of Marshall. Less than 50 miles from the popular casinos & shopping in Shreveport. Just under 12 miles from Harrison County Airport! Currently on an FHA assumable loan! Make this one yours today! Contact your trusted Realtor, & schedule your tour TODAY! For an additional 10.06 Acres See associated MLS#: 23003972
